{"tid":1837061,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"湖北赤壁市：公共交通、農村客運，省縣級客運午夜起停運","createTime":"2020-01-23T12:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T02:14:22.000Z","uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3c9ffd34ed7ada78191714ce54b434cce9f65f62","tid":1837061,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"據赤壁市人民政府網站消息，1月23日，赤壁市新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎防控指揮部發布關於城市公交、農村客運、省縣級客運暫停運營的通告。<br />\n<br />\n全文如下：<br />\n<br />\n關於城市公交、農村客運、省縣級客運暫停運營的通告<br />\n<br />\n為全力做好新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控工作，有效切斷病毒傳播途徑，堅決遏制疫情蔓延勢頭，確保人民群眾生命安全和身體健康，現將有關各項通告如下：<br />\n<br />\n自2020年1月24日0時起，赤壁市城市公交、農村客運、省縣級客運暫停運營，恢復時間另行通告。<br />\n<br />\n懇請廣大市民、旅客理解支持!<br />\n<br />\n赤壁市新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎防控指揮部<br />\n2020年1月23日"},{"pid":"f5118fac46ad0081cb316ef38f038d50d3d9a421","tid":1837061,"uid":13724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"第4個封城？"},{"pid":"a660e1ec1a9d7b5c15e99b602ca6559a55b80c11","tid":1837061,"uid":49004,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"火燒連環船<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74991605a684c2918c4e4d14375d60c3846b125","tid":1837061,"uid":23764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"整返場赤壁之戰先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ead33a94c448f0a191defe1edc4bb325ab7205","tid":1837061,"uid":76591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"赤壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b2f6aaae84ac17720793bfd8fb23685998bdf9","tid":1837061,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"今年gdp gogogo"},{"pid":"dd08a11afbc94c85ed2c95af32aba9f728ef8ef2","tid":1837061,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"火攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n疫病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ca63d8a11c645261abe7c3eda42bf80b344d4e","tid":1837061,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.616pic.com/ys_bnew_img/00/20/09/vsOnhk2xNe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.616pic.com%2Fys_bnew_img%2F00%2F20%2F09%2FvsOnhk2xNe.jpg&h=e3dafb7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"684f9f74387ef9ccefb349341355c52bc5a0c3b2","tid":1837061,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6b2f6aaae84ac17720793bfd8fb23685998bdf9","tid":1837061,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"今年gdp gogogo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"開個好年"},{"pid":"5e6b7be3516857e48adc2b4e151df323159fe797","tid":1837061,"uid":100745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WckQbnZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWckQbnZ.png&h=bc79c09c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d817d536f87a81497c4a35dbcb6fa680c3ee4a11","tid":1837061,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"疫病<br />\n而傳統評論一般沒有探究是何疫病流行。曹操將失敗原因歸於疾病，他寫信給孫權說：「赤壁之役，值有疾病，孤燒船自退，橫使周瑜虛獲此名。」見於《江表傳》，陳壽亦多次提及曹軍有疫病。<br />\n<br />\n李友松的《曹操兵敗赤壁與血吸蟲病關係之探討》一文，指出曹操赤壁之戰兵敗的原因是「疾病」&mdash;急性血吸蟲病。赤壁之戰的戰場恰恰是當時血吸蟲病嚴重流行的地區，而且時間又是血吸蟲病的感染季節。赤壁之戰是在冬天開始，但曹軍在轉徙、訓練時間是在秋天。曹軍在赤壁之戰戰前染上血吸蟲病，經過一個月以上的時間就發病了，致使大戰時疲病交加，不堪一擊。而劉、孫軍隊長期在血吸蟲流行的疫區中從事生產、生活，士兵體內或多或少已產生一定免疫力。但是這個觀點也有缺陷，曹操水軍主要來自荊州水軍，陸軍主力來自北方，荊州士兵對血吸蟲的免疫力應跟孫劉聯軍應該差別不大，所以該是其他疫病。"},{"pid":"8fc0a6a7df55c8863a168dbf52884aa802b357dd","tid":1837061,"uid":338097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ca63d8a11c645261abe7c3eda42bf80b344d4e","tid":1837061,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.616pic.com/ys_bnew_img/00/20/09/vsOnhk2xNe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.616pic.com%2Fys_bnew_img%2F00%2F20%2F09%2FvsOnhk2xNe.jpg&h=e3dafb7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"唔好向下呀<br />\n向東同北都係好選擇黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93008aeaded4c7016c9c0c51c001b782620e31ba","tid":1837061,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e6b7be3516857e48adc2b4e151df323159fe797","tid":1837061,"uid":100745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WckQbnZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWckQbnZ.png&h=bc79c09c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:41:45.000Z","msg":"興奮哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d792377cd7ea06f88eab032d732c26d5fc11f1c1","tid":1837061,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:52:11.000Z","msg":"當年曹軍都係輸起赤壁瘟疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc9800a3363a56b651d94469843977f42d997df","tid":1837061,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"過百市等住做死城"},{"pid":"a08b7f3de59a3f914df17af407d5e8153d6e65d6","tid":1837061,"uid":31031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"全境封鎖"},{"pid":"2324a062194d287cd171a0a3af676a51fa6261a7","tid":1837061,"uid":34652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"赤壁懷古<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d1abdcbdee10b672085bc826ea56eeeb5c0b76","tid":1837061,"uid":130568,"lik